ealogy   Alumni Manuscripts Civil War   New Market Preston Library Library Home Find Books Departments Media Equipment Technical Services Visitor Information Archives Archives Home Online Exhibits VMI History FAQs Genealogy   Alumni Manuscripts Civil War   New Market Preston Library Library Home Find Books Departments Media Equipment Technical Services Visitor Information Preston Library Preston Library Library Home Library Home Find Books Find Books Departments Departments Media Equipment Media Equipment Technical Services Technical Services Visitor Information Visitor Information Archives Archives Home Online Exhibits VMI History FAQs Genealogy   Alumni Manuscripts Civil War   New Market Archives Archives Archives Home Archives Home Online Exhibits Online Exhibits VMI History FAQs VMI History FAQs Genealogy   Alumni Genealogy   Alumni Manuscripts Manuscripts Civil War   New Market Civil War   New Market Give Give Close Menu Communications   Marketing News and Features Construction News Institute Report Photos   Videos Cindy Bither Administrative Assistant P   540  464 7207 F   540  464 7443 111 Smith Hall Lexington  VA 24450 Lt  Col  Kate Crossman Associate Director of Communications   Marketing Director of Online Communications Lt  Col  Kathryn  Kate  Crossman is the Director of Online Communications at VMI  She edits  designs  develops and maintains the Institute s official internet presence as well as agency and branch sites  Lt  Col  Crossman supports all VMI offices  and related organizations  as well as the VMI Foundation and Keydet Club  Crossman s role requires an understanding of various mass communication media  including web authoring  marketing  graphic design  information technologies  journalism  user experience  video  photography  and social media  Prior to her appointment at VMI  Crossman held a teaching assistant position for Media Foundations at New School University  NY  As the Assistant to the CFO at the Corcoran Gallery of Art  Crossman managed the office  worked with independent vendors and produced various print materials  At the Smithsonian Institution Archives  she coordinated the production of marketing materials  the SIA Annual Report  wrote and edited histories for the Guide to the Smithsonian Archives  supervised the Archives library as well as accessioned and managed official records for offices of General Council  Public Affairs  National Air and Space Museum  Smithsonian Science Information Exchange and Smithsonian Research Foundation  In addition  she was part of the team to create significant public exhibits at the Smithsonian Institute Archives  James Monroe Museum and Mary Washington College  M A  Media Studies  New School University  NY B A  Art History  Mary Washington College  VA Curatorial Intern at James Monroe Museum and Memorial Library  VA Assistant to Director  Mary Washington College  DuPont Galleries  VA Communications   Marketing News and Features Construction News Institute Report Photos   Videos Cindy Bither Administrative Assistant P   540  464 7207 F   540  464 7443 111 Smith Hall Lexington  VA 24450  Communications   Marketing News and Features Construction News Institute Report Photos   Videos Cindy Bither Administrative Assistant P   540  464 7207 F   540  464 7443 111 Smith Hall Lexington  VA 24450 Communications   Marketing News and Features Construction News Institute Report Photos   Videos Communications   Marketing Communications   Marketing News and Features News and Features Construction News Construction News Institute Report Institute Report Photos   Videos Photos   Videos Cindy Bither Administrative Assistant P   540  464 7207 F   540  464 7443 111 Smith Hall Lexington  VA 24450 Cindy Bither Administrative Assistant P   540  464 7207 F   540  464 7443 111 Smith Hall Lexington  VA 24450 Cindy Bither       Lt  Col  Kate Crossman Associate Director of Communications   Marketing Director of Online Communications Lt  Col  Kathryn  Kate  Crossman is the Director of 